Gauteng Premier David Makhura has signed the Township Economic Development Bill into law. Nqobile Madlala has more. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Gauteng Premier David Makhura has signed the Township Economic Development Bill into law. The new law will help South African entrepreneurs in townships have access to government funding. READ: EXCLUSIVE | Makhura wants to work with Operation Dudula In addition, this will help them while starting businesses. Watch the video above for more details on this story.